FBIS4-12462 "drnes069_n_94014" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 10 Apr 1994 LEBANON SLA Kills 3, Wounds 3 PFLP Members SLA Kills 3, Wounds 3 PFLP Members NC1004072094 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 0700 GMT 10 Apr 94 NC1004072094 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] Our military correspondent reports that a terrorist cell opened fire on an Israeli army post in 'Ali al-Tahir area yesterday afternoon. Immediately afterward, the Israeli army carried out a wide-scale combing operation in which helicopters and tanks took part. Meanwhile, South Lebanese Army personnel [SLA] manning a tank positioned in Kafr Rumman discovered the cell as it was entering a red stone villa in the town. The SLA soldiers shelled the cell, killing three elements from the Popular Front for the Liberation of Palestine [PFLP] and wounding three others.
